<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id9118178a-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2021—Par. (4). <ref href="/us/pl/116/283">Pub. L. 116–283</ref> substituted “(Z)” for “(Y)”.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id9118178b-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="shortTitle" id="id9118178c-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Short Title</heading><p><ref href="/us/pl/113/272/s1/a">Pub. L. 113–272, § 1(a)</ref>, <date date="2014-12-18">Dec. 18, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/2952">128 Stat. 2952</ref>, provided that: <quotedContent origin="/us/pl/113/272/s1/a">“This Act [enacting this chapter] may be cited as the ‘Ukraine Freedom Support Act of 2014’.”</quotedContent>
</p>
</note>
